        <h1 class="ph-title">Best Oud Perfumes in UAE You Should Try in <em>2026</em></h1>
        <p class="ph-sub">Oud is the beating heart of Gulf perfumery — deep, resinous and unmistakably luxurious. This guide breaks down what oud actually is, why it performs so well in the UAE heat, and how to choose a bottle that wears beautifully from morning majlis to midnight.</p>
